// O(n^3) time
class Solution1 {
public:
int numberOfArithmeticSlices(vector<int>& nums) {
int count = 0, n = nums.size();
for(int start = 0; start < n-2; start++) {
for(int second = start+1; second<n-1; second++) {
int diff = nums[second] - nums[start];
int prev = second;
// cout << "[" << start<<nums[start] << " " <<
// prev<<nums[second] << endl;
for(int next = prev+1; next<n; next++) {
if(nums[next] - nums[prev] == diff) {
// cout << "-> " << next<<nums[next] << endl;
prev = next;
count++;
}
}
}
}
return count;
}
};
class Solution {
public:
int numberOfArithmeticSlices(vector<int>& A) {
int n = A.size();
int res = 0;
vector<unordered_map<long long, int>> dp(n); // dp[i][d-->count]
for(int i = 1; i < n; i++) {
for(int j = 0; j < i; j++) {
long long d = (long long) A[i] - A[j];
int c = dp[j].count(d) ? dp[j][d] : 0;
dp[i][d] += c + 1;
res += c;
}
}
return res;
}
};
